{"tid":203490,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"搵人合租","createTime":"2017-04-16T10:25:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T10:51:12.000Z","uid":40775,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"48371ea046d0d7d811e6d707729bfe7a72d9d214","tid":203490,"uid":40775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T10:25:12.000Z","msg":"開左兩次post 都沉左底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原本係連登搵左人合租<br />\n但佢租左一個月之後就話唔租 放我飛機<br />\n而家又要搵另一個合租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n間屋係深水埗唐5樓 業主新裝修 280呎左右 兩房一廳 間房有啲細 有齊床褥床架 可以即入住<br />\n<br />\n租金就7500 即係每人3750 有收據睇 我冇食價 可以計平啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 起碼好過自己食哂<br />\n<br />\n另外上網就csl 無限4g plan 每月466蚊 即係每人233<br />\n<br />\n水電就 我自己一個人住就150一個月 到時平分就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳情可以add我tg傾 @M0kona <br />\n<br />\n我係紅巴 唔介意室友咩性別 正常人就得 唔好潛水 識覆msg就得<br />\n<br />\n另外我仲有隻貓 好乖好痴人好嗲"},{"pid":"a029b6432881d4431fc99171b05dbc01817efb78","tid":203490,"uid":40775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T10:26:22.000Z","msg":"留個名先"},{"pid":"4c74658d84d5b74a4ec6d1a0c4cce0fcfbd3a32f","tid":203490,"uid":97989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T10:33:38.000Z","msg":"0 /1仔?"},{"pid":"fc8909c9bd28b1905cac0b29ebe538bf769ef7ae","tid":203490,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T10:35:56.000Z","msg":"我想租 但我對腳好臭 OK?"},{"pid":"e9094367e87a1569f793103cfc529c965efdd31b","tid":203490,"uid":40775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T10:49:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>0 /1仔?</blockquote><br />\n1仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa232472f95c9d96f699e5ad741aec289fe59a4","tid":203490,"uid":53652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T10:51:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquo